C-Types

Non-standard types available for use in your C/C++ programs on this processor configuration. These types correspond to ctypes in the TIE files used in this configuration.

proto SQRT.S { out xtfloat vd, in xtfloat vs }{xtfloat f0, xtfloat f1, xtfloat f2, xtfloat f3, xtfloat f4, xtfloat f6, xtfloat f7}{
SQRT0.S f2, vs;
CONST.S f3, 0;
MADDN.S f3, f2, f2;
NEXP01.S f4, vs;
CONST.S f0, 3;
ADDEXP.S f4, f0;
MADDN.S f0, f3, f4;
NEXP01.S f3, vs;
MADDN.S f2, f0, f2;
CONST.S f0, 0;
CONST.S f6, 0;
CONST.S f7, 0;
MSUBN.S f0, f3, f2;
MADDN.S f6, f2, f4;
CONST.S f4, 3;
MADDN.S f7, f4, f2;
MADDN.S f3, f0, f0;
MADDN.S f4, f6, f2;
NEG.S f2, f7;
MADDN.S f0, f3, f2;
MADDN.S f7, f4, f7;
MKSADJ.S f2, vs;
NEXP01.S f1, vs;
MADDN.S f1, f0, f0;
NEG.S f3, f7;
ADDEXPM.S f0, f2;
ADDEXP.S f3, f2;
DIVN.S f0, f1, f3;
AE_MOV vd, f0;
}
proto SQRT.SX2 { out xtfloatx2 vd, in xtfloatx2 vs }{xtfloatx2 f0, xtfloatx2 f1, xtfloatx2 f2, xtfloatx2 f3, xtfloatx2 f4, xtfloatx2 f6, xtfloatx2 f7}{

CONST.S f3, 0;
MADDN.S f3, f2, f2;
NEXP01.S f4, vs;
CONST.S f0, 3;
ADDEXP.S f4, f0;
MADDN.S f0, f3, f4;
NEXP01.S f3, vs;
MADDN.S f2, f0, f2;
CONST.S f0, 0;

MSUBN.S f0, f3, f2;
MADDN.S f6, f2, f4;

MADDN.S f7, f4, f2;
MADDN.S f3, f0, f0;
MADDN.S f4, f6, f2;

MADDN.S f0, f3, f2;
MADDN.S f7, f4, f7;

NEXP01.S f1, vs;
MADDN.S f1, f0, f0;
NEG.S f3, f7;
